data.description: This stunning Westland ranch welcomes you before you walk in the door with its stunning landscaping all around! Inside the home you are greeted by the open and airy feeling created by the wealth of natural light flooding in from all angles of this home. The living room features cozy carpeting and tons of room for the whole family to sit around and enjoy a good movie together. Moving into the kitchen you will find a lovely dining area connected to the kitchen, you will also find gorgeous granite countertops with stainless steel appliances surrounding as well as a wealth of cabinet space! This home has an amazing flow from room to room, making entertaining a breeze! Moving into the bedrooms, you will find more cozy carpeting as well as a ceiling fan in each room for comfort all year round! The bathroom is recently updated with a lovely vanity and a new light fixture. The large, fenced-in backyard is perfect for letting the dogs run and play, having friends and family over for a bonfire on the patio, or having the kids run around! This home offers Livonia Public Schools as well.  Seller has obtained the C of O
